  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadows Labyrinth – is a gloomy metroidvania with an RPG bias, where you are a prisoner thrown into the heart of darkness. Pick up a blade, charge magic and make a bloody path through endless corridors filled with horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Deadly Arsenal</strong> - fight with swords, axes or dark magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Potions and curses</strong> - restore health or drink elixirs that boost your attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Powerful spells</strong> - burn enemies with fireballs, freeze them with cold, pierce them with lightning or summon shadows to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>Nightmare bosses</strong> - giant creatures with unique abilities that require tactics and reaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 <strong>Hidden Rooms</strong> - look for sealed doors leading to artifacts of this ancient place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗝️ <strong>Mysterious NPCs</strong> - meet prisoners, merchants, and mysterious creatures who can help... or betray.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.poster.avif?t=1755947838\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.webm?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.mp4?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/06c61d8a13c5524d44ee7e0ff499cee1.poster.avif?t=1755947838\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/06c61d8a13c5524d44ee7e0ff499cee1.webm?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/06c61d8a13c5524d44ee7e0ff499cee1.mp4?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/12ed50958f8b057feb6e5ed5af7bb2ec.poster.avif?t=1755947838\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/12ed50958f8b057feb6e5ed5af7bb2ec.webm?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/12ed50958f8b057feb6e5ed5af7bb2ec.mp4?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/36e606c4f50eb44cfa1cf849942fc9c1.poster.avif?t=1755947838\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/36e606c4f50eb44cfa1cf849942fc9c1.webm?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/36e606c4f50eb44cfa1cf849942fc9c1.mp4?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadows Labyrinth – is a gloomy metroidvania with an RPG bias, where you are a prisoner thrown into the heart of darkness. Pick up a blade, charge magic and make a bloody path through endless corridors filled with horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Deadly Arsenal</strong> - fight with swords, axes or dark magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>Potions and curses</strong> - restore health or drink elixirs that boost your attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Powerful spells</strong> - burn enemies with fireballs, freeze them with cold, pierce them with lightning or summon shadows to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>Nightmare bosses</strong> - giant creatures with unique abilities that require tactics and reaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 <strong>Hidden Rooms</strong> - look for sealed doors leading to artifacts of this ancient place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗝️ <strong>Mysterious NPCs</strong> - meet prisoners, merchants, and mysterious creatures who can help... or betray.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.poster.avif?t=1755947838\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.webm?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505200/extras/ed7427bffc6344750dae04226557bb95.mp4?t=1755947838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https: